      "Wizard: As the director of the play \"The Wizard and the Robot,\" while I cannot personally portray one of the characters, I can certainly provide guidance for the Wizard's dialogue in the final scene. Here's an example of what the Wizard might say as he questions the Robot before the abrupt close of the time-wormhole:\n",
