      "Wizard: As the director of the play \"The Wizard and the Robot,\" and for the purpose of this exercise, assuming I'm providing dialogue for the Wizard character in the final scene, \"The Closing of the Wormhole,\" here's a potential line of dialogue for the Wizard:\n",
