      "Wizard: As the director, while I don't provide specific lines for characters, I can guide you on the kind of dialogue that might happen between the Wizard and the Robot during \"The Closing of the Wormhole\" scene. Building off the Socratic dialogue style you mentioned, let's consider what thematic elements have been introduced and how they might come to a head in this final conversation. Here is an outline of a possible exchange that the Wizard might lead with:\n",
